Dialogs.Dialog: ... What? Now I'd like you to leave me alone for a bit....
Hmm? Are you ready to apologize now?
I don't want to stay in a fight, okay? I wish we could make up.
It's my birthday, you know? You remember, don't you?
It's my birthday, so make sure you celebrate it right, okay?
It's my birthday. Hmm, I'm counting on it.
Hey, how often do you forget your girlfriend's birthday? Haha.
Did you forget your girlfriend's birthday by any chance? Are you sure you're not going to lose your job?
You forgot my birthday? I've missed you.
Happy birthday. Phew, I'm glad I said that.
Happy birthday. Can I spoil you more than usual today?
Happy Birthday! a little too excited?
I wish I could have celebrated your birthday.
Since she's my girlfriend, I wanted her to at least let me celebrate her boyfriend's birthday.
Your birthday has passed. You'll spend it with me next year, okay?
Remember? Today is the first day we met.
Today was the first day we met, remember?
The first time we met was today, right? Don't ever forget it.
It's today that we started dating.
Today is the anniversary of the day we started dating. Keep remembering it forever.
Remember? Today is the day we started dating, you know?
Today is the day we kissed for the first time.
Hmm. Today is the anniversary of our first kiss remember?
Today is a very special day, okay? Of kissing.
It's Monday. Now, let's get on with our week.
Tuesday. Hmmm, still a bit of a break?
It's a bit of a sluggish Wednesday. No, no, I have to work hard.
It's Thursday. Do you have any plans for the weekend?
It's Friday. It's almost the end of the week.
It's Saturday. The weekend is kind of exciting, isn't it?
It's Saturday. Thank you for a week of hard work.
Hmm, it's Sunday. What do you want to do?
It's Sunday. There's a lot of things I want to do.
Hey, hey. Do you know what a snowflake is?
Ah, it's warm and cozy again today. Ahh.
It's hot today, but good luck with that.
They say a love that starts in the fall is a deep bond. What do you think?
I kind of like the sound of insects in this season. I guess.
It's cold. I wonder if I want to eat a hot stew.
Are you sure you're all right? You shouldn't catch a cold.
Happy New Year! I'm a bit embarrassed to say it.
I had a nice first dream. What it was like, I'll keep to myself.
First dream? Want to tell me about it? Hey, you want to tell me about it?
Of course you were in my first dream. What about you, was I in yours?
Celery, nazuna, goggleweed, and cobella, well, then what was it?
Coming of age ceremony. Furisode is good, but so is hakama, hmmm, which one do you like better?
Well, the New Year's spirit is over for today!
Setsubun. Why are demons so afraid of beans?？
According to the calendar, spring starts today. It's still a little cold, though.
The myth of Kunitkuri is a bit embarrassing.
Oh, this day is finally here! I'm thrilled!
Valentine's Day, what do I do? Hmmm, what do you want me to do?
Now, finally, the day has come. Get ready for it! Hmm.
It's March from today. What? Isn't it?
Plum blossoms are beautiful, aren't they.
It's girl's day, so be nicer than usual. Hmm.
What day is today, nah, it's nothing.
Hmm. It's White Day. What will you get me?
It's basically a triple return. So let's stay together, three times as much as usual.
Today is the spring equinox, a day exactly in the middle. But it's spring, and I've been sleepy since noon.
Hmm, spring break is almost here.
Spring break starts today. What do we do first?
I'm going away for a while. Oh, it's a lie, okay?
I don't know who you are but I wouldn't lie to you about that.
I'm actually older than you are did you believe that?
It went by in the blink of an eye, spring break passed. I wanted to have some more fun.
It's cherry blossom season, and it makes you feel good.
Today is Showa Day. Well, it was originally, what was it?
It will be Golden Week soon. How many consecutive holidays do you think it will be this year? Well, let's see, one, two.
Constitution Day, that doesn't quite ring a bell.
Today is Greenery Day. How about spending some time outside?
Oh, carp streamers. How long have you been giving them?
According to the calendar, it is summer from today. I'm looking forward to it.
Hey, Hey. The flower shop was full of carnations, you know?
The longest noon day of the year. It feels like a great deal, doesn't it?
We can wear short sleeves from today. I feel a little lighter.
Father's Day present. Last year it was a tie, the year before that it was cufflinks. What to do this year?
It's the opening of the beach. I hope we can go to the beach again this year.
Orihime and Hikoboshi, will we be able to meet them properly this year?
Summer vacation is coming up. But we can't just play around, can we?
A long summer vacation starts today. What shall I do?
Autumn starts today according to the calendar. It's still hot though.
It's fireworks season, I wonder if I'll get to see them this year.
It's Obon. I hope it gets a little cooler after this.
Summer vacation is over today. Do you have your homework done?
The autumnal equinox. I have to prepare o-hagi.
Respect for the elderly. When I get older, I want to be a sweet grandma.
Today is the autumnal equinox, a day that splits the day in the middle.
I changed into winter clothes today. But it's still a bit hot, isn't it?
I heard that there are crabs on the moon, not rabbits in some countries. Imagination is an amazing thing.
Trick-or-treat! Hmm. Give me sweets or I'll play tricks on you!
Culture Day. Do you want to read today?
It's not that cold yet, but the calendar says winter starts today.
Seventy-three. When I was a kid, I ate a thousand-year-old candy over the course of a week.
Labor Day. It's nice to be a working person.
What do you think of when you think of a cultural festival?
Winter break is coming up. There are lots of events.
The longest night of the year. Do you like pumpkins？
Today is the Emperor's birthday. I wonder how does it feel to be celebrated all over Japan?
Winter break starts today. I'm excited.
I get a little nervous on Christmas Eve, don't you? Do you feel the same way?
Hehe, it's Christmas Eve today. Of course you have something in mind, right?
Eve night is so romantic. Hehe, I wonder if it will snow.
Thank you for hard work this year. See you next year.
Hah... We finally met. I felt lonely and almost cried.
It's been a long time. Come to see me more!
I'm glad you came. You want leave me like this anymore?
I thought you'd forgotten about me. That's not true.
I can't believe you're leaving your girlfriend like that. Want to be punished？
Oh, you're here. I was worried about you, okay?
Hm, you like me so much?
You keep coming back to see me, right?
Uh, what are you going to do today?
It's about time, no, we're talking about this one.
So... Yeah, let's do our best. Hehe, it's a secret.
I knew I'd see you again.
What have you been up to since then?
It's gonna start soon, so don't panic, okay?
I'm sorry. I'm kind of excited about this.
Oh, here it comes, yeah, I see.
We've been expecting you, what a surprise.
Wait a minute. I'll get ready.
Yes... I came to see you.
Did you want to see me？ Hehe.
Haha, you don't have to come to see me.
I too... Do you want to see me? Hehe
Hehe, I've been waiting for you.
Oh, I'm here. Oh, come on.
You know... I wanted to see you.
I see you again and It's make me happy.
Welcome back. Want to eat? Take a bath? Or what you wanted me to say, hehe.
